description: TASK and SOLUTIONS PROFESSIONAL SERVICES (TSPS) REQUIREMENTOrganization Name: The Department of Foreign Affairs, Trade and Development Canada (DFATD) (also known as Global Affairs Canada (GAC))Anticipated Start Date: Upon contract award (January, 2023)Estimated level of effort: 114 days Contract Duration: from the date of the contract award to July 31, 2024Solicitation Method: CompetitiveApplicable Trade Agreements: The requirement is subject to the provisions of the Canada-Chile Free Trade Agreement, the Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement, the Canada-Honduras Free Trade Agreement, the Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement, the Canada-Panama Free Trade Agreement, and the Canadian Free Trade Agreement.
